{"tid":1781422,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡少芬求工作賺奶粉錢","createTime":"2019-12-13T06:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T09:43:18.000Z","uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2935547870682e3be8c6848238d44857800491bc","tid":1781422,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:41:27.000Z","msg":"因演出《甄嬛傳》而獲得高人氣的46歲港星蔡少芬，今年6月底宣布懷了第三胎，日前她產下兒子張樂兒，丈夫張晉開心在微博發文，表示老婆已於15日順利產子，目前母子已平安回到家中。<br />\n<br />\n鏡周刊報導，蔡少芬與老公張晉結婚11年，育有兩女，夫妻倆今年6月逗趣拍影片，另類宣布第三胎報到。喜獲麟兒後，張晉在微博上分享一家五口全家福及大手拉小手照宣布喜訊，更透露兒子名叫張樂兒：「11月15日，母子平安，歡迎張樂兒來到張家，我們平安回家啦！」<br />\n<br />\n蔡少芬直接以素顏入鏡，和張晉臉貼臉展露笑容，氣色紅潤的她，精神看起來不錯。老么張樂兒則是由二女兒抱著，一家五口看起來非常幸福。<br />\n<br />\n至於還會再生第4胎嗎？蔡少芬笑稱其實六年前已經宣布「封肚不生了」，第三胎真的是一個美麗的意外，他也開玩笑說道，「雖然多生一個了，打工仔依舊繼續做」，還呼籲大家開公司仲開戲俾佢拍，讓她賺奶粉錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOV6UH2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOV6UH2.jpg&h=293bd7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hh6JWWo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhh6JWWo.jpg&h=3509fde2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PRFeH8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PRFeH8.gif&h=da7788c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xbCQBWw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxbCQBWw.gif&h=5fd1f3b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvUWxuU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgvUWxuU.gif&h=785ce8cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6907e46a9d9aedc749bf7b48ce191eace01f71d","tid":1781422,"uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"洪欣入黎未"},{"pid":"4f1468dce62f411a14f85e3f400f76d745aa5bd4","tid":1781422,"uid":48905,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"b6907e46a9d9aedc749bf7b48ce191eace01f71d","tid":1781422,"uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T06:5